                    <comment id="12380203" author="bin.chen@sabre-holdings.com" created="Tue, 22 Apr 2003 23:15:14 +0100"  >Created an attachment (id=5952)&lt;br/&gt;
Changed SSLProtocolSocketFactory.java&lt;br/&gt;
